colonial
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a European resident of NZ; a non-Maori native-born New Zealander; a person who lives in a colony; one born, or resident, outside the home country
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
